   <talk_paragraph index="n1504_hound_ghost-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1504_hound_ghost-1-a" mid="10" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Can you summarize it in one sentence please?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Ghost Hound$<BR>Only Loffy, who call himself my master but whom I consider a "partner" has talked to me and we were searching for the secrets of this world….</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1504_hound_ghost-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1504_hound_ghost-1-b" mid="12" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>The Monolith?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Ghost Hound$<BR>Young ones have no patience… I'm saying that Loffy was the only one who could see me, but he went mad and he can't communicate with me anymore.<BR>His body is here, but his soul was lost somewhere near the Monolith.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1504_hound_ghost-1-b" image="QN_Npc_Beggar.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1504_hound_ghost-1-c" mid="14" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>He has been to the Monolith?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Ghost Hound$<BR>Loffy was a captain of the pirates. He explored the world with his crew in search for great hidden treasures. But in the journey, he came across an unfortunate incident and his soul was separated from his body. You see that mad man beside me? That's just an empty shell.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1504_hound_ghost-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1504_hound_ghost-1-d" mid="16" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(How did he open the door…?)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Ghost Hound$<BR>Yeah I think that's what the place was called. Lipius and the elf queen called it the Heart of Goddess Altea. But when the door opened, what we felt was that it was none other than hell. I died there and became a ghost.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1504_hound_ghost-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1504_hound_ghost-1-e" mid="18" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Ghost Hound$<BR>Though I lost my body, I tried to go back there several times to find Loffy's soul. But I was stuck here next to Loffy's body. Maybe it's because I can't leave this body alone…</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1504_hound_ghost-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1504_hound_ghost-2" mid="20" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>How?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Ghost Hound$<BR>So… since you can see me, why don't you help me? Help me find Loffy's soul.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1504_hound_ghost-2" image="QW_94.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Ghost Hound$<BR>It must still be around the Monolith. Can you go and search the area?<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Try going to the Watcher's Tower)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1624_lifius-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1624_lifius-2-a" mid="23" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Who are you?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$???$<BR>It has been a long time since I met an intelligent being. Do you mind if I join you in this long journey?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1624_lifius-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1624_lifius-3" mid="25" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$???$<BR>…I'm sorry, I can't hear very well. Why don't you come a little closer so that I can read your lips?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1624_lifius-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1624_lifius-3-a" mid="27" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Isn't that the name of Loffy's girlfriend…?)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n1624_lifius-3-a" mid="28" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>How did you enter this place?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Lipius$<BR>My name is <FONT color=#a82424>Lipius</FONT>.<BR>I'm a Walker.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1624_lifius-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1624_lifius-3-b" mid="30" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What do you mean? You have to keep walking?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Lipius$<BR>I am walking because walking is all I can do.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1624_lifius-3-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1624_lifius-3-c" mid="32" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Do you know a pirate named Loffy?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$Lipius$<BR>What are you looking for in this place?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1624_lifius-3-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1624_lifius-3-d" mid="34" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>How about answering my question first…?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>$Lipius$<BR>I may also be searching for something like you. I thought I found my telesia, but maybe the whole journey of searching for something could be my telesia too.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1624_lifius-3-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1624_lifius-3-e" mid="36" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Did you… forget?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>$Lipius$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Lipius stares at you for a while)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1624_lifius-3-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1624_lifius-3-f" mid="38" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Erm… hello?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$Lipius$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Lipius continues to stare at you)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1624_lifius-3-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1624_lifius-3-g" mid="40" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Are you just pretending you can't hear me?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$Lipius$<BR>I'm sorry, I can't hear very well. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1624_lifius-3-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1624_lifius-4" mid="42" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Well...Okay...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="41"><![CDATA[<html>$Lipius$<BR>I'm not pretending. I really can't hear very well...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1504_hound_ghost-4" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1504_hound_ghost-4-a" mid="44" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#2b2723>(Tell him that though you didn't find Loffy, you met Lipius)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>$Ghost Hound$<BR>You're back! So did you find Loffy's soul?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1504_hound_ghost-4-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1504_hound_ghost-4-b" mid="46" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#086171>Receive Reward</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
