   <talk_paragraph index="n1504_hound_ghost-4-b" image="QN_Npc_lifius.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1504_hound_ghost-4-c" mid="48" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>He was a man.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>$Ghost Hound$<BR>…What?! You met the elf Lipius who calls himself the Walker?!<BR>You mean the Lipius who's the best friend of Loffy whom everyone thought was his girlfriend??!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1504_hound_ghost-4-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1504_hound_ghost-4-!next" mid="50" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I see.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="49"><![CDATA[<html>$Ghost Hound$<BR>People thought Lipius was Loffy's girlfriend because he was too pretty. If it's an elf who's beautiful enough to be passed off as a lady and who calls himself the Walker… he must be the Lipius that I know.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1624_lifius-4" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="51"><![CDATA[<html>$Lipius$<BR>The breeze is gentle today. The Goddess must be happy to see you here too.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Looks like you can't get any information about Loffy from him)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
